headline: Zimmer Biomet Welcomes Arnold Schwarzenegger as Chief Movement Officer
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH), a global medical technology leader, today announced a partnership with Arnold Schwarzenegger, who will take on the newly established role of Chief Movement Officer. In this strategic role, Schwarzenegger will collaborate closely with Zimmer Biomet to motivate, engage and support individuals to increase mobility, maintain joint health and proactively incorporate movement into their daily routines to foster overall health and wellness.
